text.tspan: Share of male vs. female employment in services, 2022
The horizontal axis shows female employment in services as a share of total female employment. The vertical
axis shows male employment in services as a share of total male employment. The services sector consists of
retail trade, restaurants and hotels; transport, storage, and communications; financing, insurance, real estate,
and business services; and community, social, and personal services.
